MemberSignature.Value: .method public hidebysig instance string[] RemoveRootsWithSharedOutputs(class Microsoft.Build.Framework.ITaskItem[] sources) cil managed
Public Function RemoveRootsWithSharedOutputs (sources As ITaskItem()) As String()

param.name: sources
param.span: 构成根标记（其输出不应是由任何其他根标记共享的）的源集。

span.span: The set of sources that form the rooting marker whose outputs should not be shared by any other rooting marker.

summary.span: 假如有源集，则从依赖项关系图中移除任何与从给定源集构造的根标记共享相同输出的根。

span.span: Given a set of sources, removes from the dependency graph any roots that share the same outputs as the rooting marker constructed from the given set of sources.

returns.span: 已删除的根标记的数组。

span.span: An array of the rooting markers that were removed.

comment.span: 如果有多个输入集可能生成相同的输出，则使用此方法，这是使生成相同输出的任何其他根的失效的一种方法，以便在下次运行该任务时，不会错误地认为它是最新的。

span.span: Used when there's a possibility that more than one set of inputs may produce the same output -- this is a way to invalidate any other roots that produce that same outputs, so that the next time the task is run with that other set of inputs, it won't incorrectly believe that it is up-to-date.
